text: Schuttertal is a municipality in Ortenau in Baden-Württemberg, Germany. It is in the Schutter Valley in Black Forest. Schuttertal was created in 1974 from the former municipalities Schuttertal, Dörlinbach and Schweighausen. == References == == Other websites == * Schuttertal's Official Website Category:Ortenaukreis
